title: MEIOU and Taxes v1.16 EU4 mod
description:
MEIOU and Taxes v1.16 EU4 mod


Extract 7zip file into your C:Users [user] Documents Paradox Interactive Europa Universalis IV mod folder




Welcome to MEIOU and Taxes, an EUIV total conversion mod brought about by the merger of the EUIII mods, Death and Taxes and MEIOU, and brought to you by Lukew, Gigau, DHarper, Sun Wu and the M&T team. 

This mod contains 970 new provinces and 450 new nations. Almost every aspect of the game has been either reworked or completely redone, with a new map, new trade system, new musical score, redone graphics and a totally reworked religious system.
